tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE RetinaScanningData (
  participant_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  x_coordinate INT,
  y_coordinate INT,
  scan_data BYTEA
);

CREATE TABLE ResearchStudies (
  study_id INT,
  study_name VARCHAR(255),
  researcher_id INT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE EyeMovementPatterns (
  pattern_id INT,
  participant_id INT,
  pattern_type VARCHAR(50),
  pattern_description TEXT,
  pattern_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE Retina_Scanning_Sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_id INT,
    session_date DATE,
    duration_minutes INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES Retina_Scanning_Participants(participant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Retina_Scanning_Data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT,
    scan_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    x_coordinate FLOAT,
    y_coordinate FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES Retina_Scanning_Sessions(session_id)
);
